## HarFormatEntry.\_kassetteMockKey property

Key used by kassette to select the correct mock to replay.

**Signature:**

```typescript
_kassetteMockKey?: string;
```

## Remarks

This field contains the value passed to [IMock.setMockHarKey()](./kassette.imock.setmockharkey.md) when used with the default [mocksHarKeyManager](./kassette.configurationspec.mocksharkeymanager.md)<!-- -->.
